<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Registration Successful</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #3b82f6;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    .body {
      padding: 24px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .body p {
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #fafafa;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #3b82f6;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .header h1 { font-size: 16px; }
      .body p { font-size: 12px; }
      .footer p { font-size: 10px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to The Easy Mart 🎉</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

      <p>Your account has been successfully created on <strong>The Easy Mart</strong>.</p>

      <p>We’re excited to welcome you to our community!</p>

      <p>Please activate your account and start exploring amazing products and exclusive deals.</p>

      <p>If your account is not activated yet, please contact the admin for verification and activation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@The Easy Mart.com">support@The Easy Mart.com</a></p>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> - Nasi Digital Pvt Ltd</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
